node.text:
The title is about the changing world we are living in regards to climate change. Some of the glaciers you see here will literally be gone in 5 to 10 years - yes it is going that quickly.

This was the first video I made, all recorded with a Mavic Pro in Southern Greenland during summer. Technically it isn't anything groundbreaking but I really enjoyed putting all the clips with Premiere Pro together. 
I have done more projects recently but will also do some in the future, both in front and behind the camera and I'm also open for collaborations.

It’s been a pleasure to see all your creative and unique edits!

Let’s congratulate our winners:

You’ve won the Tamron lens, 500px Pro Membership, Luminar X Membership and LuminarAI!

2️⃣nd place – Lukas @wukasz.p

The backpack bundle by Peak Design, 500px Pro Membership, Luminar X Membership, and LuminarAI are yours!

3️⃣rd place – Mohammad Ilyas @mibadventurez

Enjoy the tripod from the Benro Induro collection, 500px Pro Membership, Luminar X Membership,  and LuminarAI!

Thanks to our amazing partners @tamronusa, @peakdesign, @benrousa, @500px

Stay tuned for more challenges!🚀

node.text:
Hi guys, how is everyone doing?  It’s time to get creative with LuminarAI! I'm very proud to announce the new #creativeeditingchallenge with @skylum_global.  

Show us your editing skills for a chance to win a Tamron lens, a backpack bundle by Peak Design, a tripod from the Benro Induro collection, 500px Pro Membership, Luminar X Membership, and a LuminarAI license.
Download raw images taken by Max Rive along with a free trial of LuminarAI.
Edit the images in your own creative way, replacing the sky with the provided images or your own sky.
Follow @maxrivephotography @skylum_global @500px @tamronusa @peakdesign @benrousa.
Share your edits on Instagram, tagging @maxrivephotography and @skylum_global and using the hashtag #creativeeditingchallenge.

I can’t wait to see all your stunning edits!

Thanks to our amazing partners @500px, @tamronusa, @peakdesign, @benrousa.

Check the link in bio for more details!
